### ================================================
###  Smart Parking — AI Integration Test Suite
###  Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar
### ================================================

### 1. Login (get token for protected routes)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "AdminPassword123"
}

### Extract token from login response
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}


### ================================================
###  AI Pass-Through Routes (via Backend)
### ================================================

### 2. AI Health Check (via backend)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/ai/health


### 3. Predict Demand (via backend)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ai/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hour": 14,
  "horizon": 5
}


### ================================================
###  Parking Detect Route (via Backend → AI)
### ================================================

### 4. Detect Vehicle + Plate (requires auth)
# Uses a minimal 1x1 red JPEG as base64
POST http://localhost:8000/api/parking/detect
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "imageBase64": "/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQAAAQABAAD/2wBDAAMCAgMCAgMDAwMEAwMEBQgFBQQEBQoHBwYIDAoMCwsKCwsNDhIQDQ4RDgsLEBYQERMUFRUVDA8XGBYUGBIUFRT/wAALCAABAAEBAREA/8QAFAABAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAACf/EABQQAQAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAD/2gAIAQEAAD8AVN//2Q=="
}


### 5. Detect — Missing imageBase64 (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/parking/detect
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}


### 6. Detect — No auth token (should return 401)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/parking/detect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageBase64": "/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQAAAQABAAD/2wBDAAMCAgMCAgMDAwMEAwMEBQgFBQQEBQoHBwYIDAoMCwsKCwsNDhIQDQ4RDgsLEBYQERMUFRUVDA8XGBYUGBIUFRT/wAALCAABAAEBAREA/8QAFAABAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAACf/EABQQAQAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAD/2gAIAQEAAD8AVN//2Q=="
}


### ================================================
###  Direct AI Microservice Calls (port 9000)
### ================================================

### 7. Direct AI Health
GET http://localhost:9000/ai/health


### 8. Direct LPR Recognize (base64 form)
POST http://localhost:9000/ai/lpr/recognize
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

image_b64=/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQAAAQABAAD/2wBDAAMCAgMCAgMDAwMEAwMEBQgFBQQEBQoHBwYIDAoMCwsKCwsNDhIQDQ4RDgsLEBYQERMUFRUVDA8XGBYUGBIUFRT/wAALCAABAAEBAREA/8QAFAABAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAACf/EABQQAQAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAD/2gAIAQEAAD8AVN//2Q==


### 9. Direct Vehicle Classification (base64 form)
POST http://localhost:9000/ai/vehicle/classify
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

image_b64=/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQAAAQABAAD/2wBDAAMCAgMCAgMDAwMEAwMEBQgFBQQEBQoHBwYIDAoMCwsKCwsNDhIQDQ4RDgsLEBYQERMUFRUVDA8XGBYUGBIUFRT/wAALCAABAAEBAREA/8QAFAABAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAACf/EABQQAQAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAD/2gAIAQEAAD8AVN//2Q==


### 10. Direct Demand Prediction
POST http://localhost:9000/ai/predict/demand
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hour": 14,
  "horizon": 5
}
